description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP reacts to Urban Meyer's dismissal from Jacksonville. Was it long overdue> Pro Football Hall of Fame Coach Jimmy Johnson joins us to discuss what it was like to adjust from coaching in College to the NFL. And Albert Breer calls in to give potential replacement options for Urban with the Jaguars.
